response.original_title: สุญญกาลวิมานหมอก
response.overview: The story of an ordinary day in the life of a young boy who must attend cram school to prepare for a military academy exam, as expected by his father, alongside the story of two soldiers who flee and share an intimate moment together in the forest. These two timelines overlap through drifting smoke, the sound of firecrackers, and gunshots.
response.title: สุญญกาลวิมานหมอก
